            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "泰民@SHINee與舞者NO:ZE街頭攬抱拍拖斷正 粉絲震怒要求交代",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"泰民@SHINee與29歲美女舞者NO:ZE拍拖斷正 粉絲震怒要求交代\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/1f5192a5a8e8ef3d10abd2102658e26a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250416/_2025041617104336955.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">泰民@SHINee與29歲美女舞者NO:ZE拍拖斷正 粉絲震怒要求交代</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>31歲韓團SHINee成員泰民與29歲美女舞者NO:ZE過去傳緋聞，最近二人更疑似拍拖斷正，甜蜜親暱照在網上瘋傳，引發粉絲怒潮。近日有疑似泰民和NO:ZE約會照在網上瘋傳，相中可見二人不但親密撓手散步，更有男方從女方背後抱抱的偶像劇場面。\n\n</p><h2>泰民粉絲震怒網上洗版</h2>\n<p>而從拍到正面的畫面中依稀可見，相中主角的確跟泰民、NO:ZE樣貌極之相似。有網民估計是泰民先前邀請女友看演唱會，再一起出席慶功宴後，相偕離去時被拍下約會照。有粉絲怒極留言道：「（當時）粉絲正在零下10度的仁川，一邊凍到震一邊排隊等接駁車，李泰民你如果還有良心，就該出來道歉和解釋。」泰民所屬經理人公司Big Planet Made娛樂則回應指，對泰民的戀愛傳聞正在確認中。其實粉絲圈已曾多次揣測二人之關係，作為與SM娛樂長期合作的舞者，NO:ZE與團體仍屬SM旗下的泰民常有接觸。過去NO:ZE透過偶像社交平台Bubble跟粉絲傾偈時，被指背後有疑似泰民的聲音。泰民在演唱會上作出戴戒指的表演，亦被解讀成向女友隔空示愛「求婚」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198834/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"31歲SHINee成員泰民疑似拍拖斷正。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d57d7e6aa65e6d48b42f071a36774bb9/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_31_58.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        31歲SHINee成員泰民疑似拍拖斷正。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198835/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"泰民傳聞中的戀愛對象，正是曾跟他傳緋聞的美女舞者NO:ZE。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c6ff5d3545216b77cf3b9c3c731a269e/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_32_14.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        泰民傳聞中的戀愛對象，正是曾跟他傳緋聞的美女舞者NO:ZE。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198836/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網上瘋傳疑似二人溫馨拍拖照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/41e090055ced43294f008e21e617e690/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_32_27.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網上瘋傳疑似二人溫馨拍拖照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198837/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被指是泰民的男子從後伸手攬實女友，場面浪漫媲美偶像劇。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cefc185ae4879d2d027c394490c77a3c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_33_08.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被指是泰民的男子從後伸手攬實女友，場面浪漫媲美偶像劇。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198838/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"從拍到女方正面的畫面中，可見其樣貌的確好似NO:ZE。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/325a55b462a655a8142d96e47e89c803/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_33_27.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        從拍到女方正面的畫面中，可見其樣貌的確好似NO:ZE。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198839/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"至於該名跟女友約會開心到甜笑的男子，亦有7、8成似泰民。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f691686ebbf89df66378c615706666a1/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_33_51.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        至於該名跟女友約會開心到甜笑的男子，亦有7、8成似泰民。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198840/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"SHINee雖於8年前痛失成員鐘鉉，但變成4人團後依然人氣不減。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b1c5e78b38bed3cbf532d89b37d9eeee/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_34_17.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        SHINee雖於8年前痛失成員鐘鉉，但變成4人團後依然人氣不減。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198841/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"NO:ZE於2021年帶領團隊WAYB參加《Street Woman Fighter》而爆紅。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ec340dea1e8e8903d162424c06978b81/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_34_36.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        NO:ZE於2021年帶領團隊WAYB參加《Street Woman Fighter》而爆紅。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198842/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"NO:ZE有樣有身材有舞藝，可惜曾鬧出廣告風波及耍大牌新聞，以致形象插水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3dedf82561eabb6e58d3b21cbb1ba687/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_35_29.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        NO:ZE有樣有身材有舞藝，可惜曾鬧出廣告風波及耍大牌新聞，以致形象插水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4198843/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"因負面新聞一度要暫停活動的NO:ZE，復出後首項工作就是為泰民歌曲《Guilty》伴舞。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a56dccd9975a919b5783f8d39df29b91/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-16_at_14_36_05.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        因負面新聞一度要暫停活動的NO:ZE，復出後首項工作就是為泰民歌曲《Guilty》伴舞。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>NO:ZE形象負面</h2>\n<p>作為男偶像「公然拍拖」，自然惹起粉絲大怒！尤其是NO:ZE憑跳舞節目《Street Woman Fighter》走紅後，卻惹出收了錢不發文的廣告風波，以及拍攝時耍大牌之醜聞，一度被逼暫停演藝活動，形象負面的NO:ZE自然未能討得男方粉絲歡心。不過亦有部分粉絲認為泰民已年過30，拍拖亦好正常，並聲言只希望他幸福。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
